<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta name="description" content="HiveHelper, helping beekeepers manage their hives with ease.">
    <%- include('../partials/head') %>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../partials/navbar') %>
    <main>
        <h1>Welcome to HiveHelper, <%= username %>!</h1>
        <h2>Select a navigation item below to navigate</h2>
        <a href="/livehealth">Live Health - See the live health statistics of your bee hives</a>
        <a href="/hives">Hives - View, create, or delete your bee hives</a>
        <a href="/schedule">Schedule - View, create, or delete events in your schedule</a>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
        Copyright &copy; 2024 HiveHelper & Joey Manani. <a href="https://cdn.theflyingrat.com/LICENSE">Licensing</a>
        <br>
        Dedicated for Richard Smith, expert beekeeper since 2001. 
    </footer>
    <style>
        h2 { font-size: 1.7rem }
        main > a { font-size: 1.4rem; display: block; margin: 15px 5px 0 0; color: var(--accent)}
        main > a:hover { filter: brightness(40%); }
        footer { font-size: 1.4rem; bottom: 1vh; margin-left: 15px; position: absolute; width: calc(100% - 15px); text-align: center;}
        footer > a { color: initial }
        @media only screen and (max-width: 604px) {
            h1 { font-size: 2.1rem }
            h2 { font-size: 1.3rem }
        }
    </style>
</body>
</html>
    